organic.title: Home - NM Commission for the Blind
organic.snippet: The Mission of the New Mexico Commission for the Blind is to enable persons who are blind to achieve vocational, economic and social equality.

organic.title: Adult Orientation Center - NM Commission for the Blind
organic.snippet: The Center is a certified and accredited residential program designed to equip blind persons with the skills needed to become employed.

organic.title: NMSBVI Orientation & Mobility Inventory
